      "text": "- `externally-managed-environment`: use the `.venv` steps above instead of installing into system Python.\n- `503 No healthy backend available`: check `EMBED_BACKENDS` and backend service availability.\n- `429 Gateway busy`: increase `ADMISSION_MAX_CONCURRENT` or `ADMISSION_WAIT_TIMEOUT_MS`.",
